        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                <h3>Overview </h3>
<p>While it is true Singapore is considered one of the wealthiest city-state's in Asia, global media coverage rarely focuses on parts of the society that do not indulge in the wealthy excesses of the Singapore elite. This short clip from CNA Insider focuses on one of these residents: the hard-working gas pump attendant.</p>
<h3>Origin</h3>
<p>Singapore</p>
<p> <div class="post__iframe"><iframe width="600" height="450" style="border: 0;" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d255281.2256037751!2d103.67910045891549!3d1.3139945933947381!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da11238a8b9375%3A0x887869cf52abf5c4!2sSingapore!5e0!3m2!1sen!2snl!4v1688803281148!5m2!1sen!2snl" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe></div>
<h3>The other sight of Singapore</h3>
<figure class="post__video"><iframe loading="lazy" width="560" height="314" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IE-WudlDTnE" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe></figure>
<h3>Reflect</h3>
<ul>
<li>Based on Halid's story, how different are the gas pump attendants in your area?</li>
<li>How did you feel about Halid? Were you impressed with his work ethic, or did you feel sorry for him?</li>
</ul>
<h3>Explore</h3>
<p>Channel News Asia. (2020, February 15). <em>Going hungry in Singapore, a cheap food paradise</em>. Retrieved from CNA Insider: https://youtu.be/PQaVds_uFDY</p>
