<p>Chuang, T. (1889). <em>Chuang Tzu: Mystic, moralist, and social reformer</em>. Retrieved from Gutenberg.org: https://gutenberg.org/cache/epub/59709/pg59709-images.html</p>
<p>Chuang, T. (1974). <em>Chuang Tsu: Inner chapters.</em> Vintage.</p>
