                    This playlist provides an overview of how teachers and students can be introduced to Asian literature and media. This playlist&hellip;
                ]]>
            </summary>
        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                    <p><img src="https://bartob03.github.io/SJSUInfo23710/media/posts/2/main.png" class="type:primaryImage" alt="Introduction to Asian Literature and Media playlist " /></p>
                <p>This playlist provides an overview of how teachers and students can be introduced to Asian literature and media. This playlist is designed to meet the competencies and domains as they are described in the <a href="https://standards.aasl.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/AASL-Standards-Framework-for-Learners-pamphlet.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AASL Standards Framework for Learners</a>.  </p>
<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; border-style: groove; height: 158.312px;" border="1">
<tbody>
<tr style="height: 79.1562px;">
<td style="width: 6.86118%;"><strong> </strong></td>
<td style="width: 26.6624%; height: 79.1562px;"><strong>Activity</strong></td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%; height: 79.1562px;"><strong>AASL Competency and Domain</strong></td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%; height: 79.1562px;"><strong>Notes</strong></td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 79.1562px;">
<td style="width: 6.86118%;">1</td>
<td style="width: 26.6624%; height: 79.1562px;">Read the titles of the posts in the <a href="https://bartob03.github.io/SJSUInfo23710/sjsu-info-237-sec-10-curriculum-text-sets.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Table of Contents page</a> and then click any of the <a href="https://bartob03.github.io/SJSUInfo23710/sjsu-info-237-sec-10-curriculum-text-sets.html">links</a>  to get started.</td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%; height: 79.1562px;">Participate in an activity designed to help you think, create, share, and grow independently and within a learning community.</td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%; height: 79.1562px;"> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 6.86118%;">2</td>
<td style="width: 26.6624%;">Click the map embedded on the post to check the origin of the content. You can also open <a href="https://earth.google.com/web/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Earth</a> to further explore the region.</td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%;">
<p><strong>Explore</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Exercise information gathering skills by choosing the right tools and sources.</li>
<li>Engage curiosity and actively acquire new knowledge.</li>
</ul>
</td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%;"> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 6.86118%;">3</td>
<td style="width: 26.6624%;">Read, listen, or watch the content.</td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%;">
<p><strong>Inquire, Include, Collaborate, Curate</strong></p>
<p>Experience content that is beyond mainstream media and literature. Engage and participate within a completely different paradigm.</p>
</td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%;"> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 6.86118%;">4</td>
<td style="width: 26.6624%;">
<p>Read the guided question and write down what comes to mind.</p>
<p>If you have your own questions about the content, write them down too.</p>
</td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%;">
<p><strong>Inquire - Create</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Formulate questions about a topic.</li>
<li>Demonstrate curiosity with a new topic or theme.</li>
</ul>
</td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%;"> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 6.86118%;">5</td>
<td style="width: 26.6624%;">Discuss your ideas and opinions of the content with your peers or your instructor.</td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%;">
<p><strong>Include - Think, Create, Share</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Interact with other learners and individuals with different ideas, perspectives, and backgrounds.</li>
<li>Engage in informed conversation and debate.</li>
</ul>
</td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%;"> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 6.86118%;">6</td>
<td style="width: 26.6624%;">Explore suggested readings or media related to the content.</td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%;">
<p><strong>Inquire - Grow</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Seek additional information and continue inquiry.</li>
<li>Exercise understanding through additional resources.</li>
</ul>
</td>
<td style="width: 33.2382%;"> </td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
